---
title: Quick Teriyaki Chicken Noodles with Asian Greens & Peanuts
description: Packed full of protein, this Asian chicken and noodle dish is the perfect energy boost you need to hit the gym, football field or
swimming pool. With the addition of aromatic ginger lemongrass paste and crunchy peanuts, you're in for a quickly cooked taste
sensation that'll have you running for more.
